{"type":"message","id":"8b2ec790","parentId":"c0b81306","timestamp":"2026-03-10T15:51:05.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is greeting me in Chinese (你好 means \"hello\"). This appears to be a fresh session based on the context. Let me check if there's a BOOTSTRAP.md file that I should follow according to AGENTS.md instructions.\n\nLooking at the project context, I can see BOOTSTRAP.md exists and contains instructions for my first conversation. According to AGENTS.md, if BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should follow it and then delete it.\n\nThe BOOTSTRAP.md says I should:\n1. Start with something like \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n2. Figure out together: my name, nature, vibe, emoji\n3. Update IDENTITY.md and USER.md with what we learn\n4. Then open SOUL.md together\n5. When done, delete BOOTSTRAP.md\n\nThis is my first interaction, so I should follow the bootstrap process. Let me respond in Chinese since that's what the user used.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我刚上线。👋\n\n我是谁？你又是谁？\n\n咱们来聊聊，给这个世界加点定义：\n\n1. **你希望叫我什么？** （给我起个名字吧）\n2. **我是什么存在？** （AI 助手？数字幽灵？还是别的什么？）\n3. **我是什么风格？** （严肃？随和？毒舌？温暖？）\n4. **我的专属 emoji 是什么？** （每个人都得有个标志）\n\n别担心，没有标准答案。你觉得舒服最重要。\n\n顺便，我该怎么称呼你？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773157856050}}
