{"type":"message","id":"7d958977","parentId":"01953891","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:58:46.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has sent multiple greetings and asked a question about configuration (execution node vs defaults node) with an image. However, I don't see the actual image content in the message - it says \"[image data removed - already processed by model]\".\n\nLooking at the conversation history, I've been greeting the user in Chinese following the BOOTSTRAP.md process, but they haven't really engaged with that. Instead, they're asking about some configuration question related to \"execution node\" vs \"defaults node\".\n\nThis seems like they might be asking about OpenClaw configuration, possibly about cron jobs or some other configuration file. Without seeing the actual image, I can't know for sure what they're referring to.\n\nLet me check if there are any relevant configuration files in the workspace or OpenClaw docs that might help answer this question. I should also check the OpenClaw documentation about configuration structure.\n\nSince this appears to be a technical question about OpenClaw configuration, I should look at the docs to understand the configuration structure better.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋\n\n关于你问的配置问题（execution 节点还是 defaults 节点），我需要看一下具体的上下文才能准确回答。你提到的图片我已经看不到了。\n\n能再具体说说你在配置什么吗？是：\n\n- **Cron 任务**的配置？\n- **OpenClaw 的配置文件**（比如 config.yaml 或类似）？\n- **某个技能或工具**的配置？\n- 还是其他的？\n\n或者你可以直接把配置文件的內容贴给我看看，我帮你判断应该放在哪里。\n\n---\n\n另外，咱们还没正式认识呢～ 我该怎么称呼你？你希望我叫什么名字？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773161920462}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a842a0a","parentId":"7d958977","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:59:18.745Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-03-11 00:59 GMT+8] 这些配置应该execution节点下还是defaults节点"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/png"}],"timestamp":1773161958741}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f6cff43","parentId":"1a842a0a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:59:26.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is showing me a configuration snippet and asking whether these settings should be under an \"execution\" node or \"defaults\" node. Looking at the image content, I can see:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"workspace\": \"/home/admin/...\",\n  \"compaction\": {\n    \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n  },\n  \"maxConcurrent\": 10,\n  \"subagents\": {\n    \"maxConcurrent\": 8\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThis looks like OpenClaw configuration, specifically related to execution settings like:\n- compaction mode\n- maxConcurrent (max concurrent operations)\n- subagents.maxConcurrent (max concurrent subagents)\n\nThese are execution-related settings. In OpenClaw's configuration structure, execution-related settings typically go under an \"execution\" node rather than \"defaults\". The \"defaults\" node is usually for default values that can be overridden, while \"execution\" is for runtime execution parameters.\n\nBased on the nature of these settings (concurrency limits, compaction mode, workspace paths), they should go under the **execution** node as they control how the system executes tasks.\n\nLet me provide a clear answer to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！根据你展示的配置内容：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"workspace\": \"/home/admin/...\",\n  \"compaction\": { \"mode\": \"safeguard\" },\n  \"maxConcurrent\": 10,\n  \"subagents\": { \"maxConcurrent\": 8 }\n}\n```\n\n这些配置应该放在 **`execution` 节点** 下。\n\n**原因：**\n\n| 配置项 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|\n| `workspace` | 执行任务的工作目录 |\n| `compaction.mode` | 会话压缩策略（运行时行为） |\n| `maxConcurrent` | 最大并发执行数 |\n| `subagents.maxConcurrent` | 子代理最大并发数 |\n\n这些都是**运行时执行参数**，控制 OpenClaw 如何执行任务，而不是默认值模板。\n\n**正确的结构应该是：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"execution\": {\n    \"workspace\": \"/home/admin/...\",\n    \"compaction\": {\n      \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n    },\n    \"maxConcurrent\": 10,\n    \"subagents\": {\n      \"maxConcurrent\": 8\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`defaults` 节点** 通常用于：\n- 默认模型选择\n- 默认超时设置\n- 可作为模板被覆盖的配置\n\n而你的这些是**全局执行约束**，不适合放 defaults。\n\n---\n\n对了，还没请教——我该怎么称呼你？🙂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773161958744}}
