oSession()`:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:320:`limitHistoryTurns()` trims conversation history base\r\nd on channel type (DM vs group).\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:321:\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:322:### Compaction\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:323:\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:324:Auto-compaction triggers on context overflow. `compac\r\ntEmbeddedPiSessionDirect()` handles manual compaction:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:325:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:326:```typescript\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:384:OpenClaw loads custom pi extensions for specialized b\r\nehavior:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:385:\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:386:### Compaction Safeguard\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:387:\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:388:`src/agents/pi-extensions/compaction-safeguard.ts` ad\r\nds guardrails to compaction, including adaptive token budgeting plus tool failure and file operation summaries:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:389:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:390:```typescript\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:391:if (resolveCompactionMode(params.cfg) === \"safeguard\"\r\n) {\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:392:  setCompactionSafeguardRuntime(params.sessionManager\r\n, { maxHistoryShare });\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:393:  paths.push(resolvePiExtensionPath(\"compaction-safeg\r\nuard\"));\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:394:}\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:395:```\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:448:```typescript\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:449:isContextOverflowError(errorText)     // Context too \r\nlarge\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:450:isCompactionFailureError(errorText)   // Compaction f\r\nailed\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:451:isAuthAssistantError(lastAssistant)   // Auth failure\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:452:isRateLimitAssistantError(...)        // Rate limited\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:478:  config: params.config,\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:479:  sessionKey: sandboxSessionKey,\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:480:  workspaceDir: resolvedWorkspace,\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:481:});\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:482:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\prose.md:77:## File locations\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\prose.md:78:\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\prose.md:79:OpenProse keeps state under `.prose/` in your works\r\npace:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\prose.md:80:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\prose.md:81:```\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:42:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:43:If multiple providers are configured, the selected pr\r\novider is used first and the others are fallback options.\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:44:Auto-summary uses the configured `summaryModel` (or `\r\nagents.defaults.model.primary`),\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:45:so that provider must also be authenticated if you en\r\nable summaries.\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:46:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:209:- If `provider` is **unset**, OpenClaw prefers `open\r\nai` (if key), then `elevenlabs` (if key),\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:210:  otherwise `edge`.\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:211:- `summaryModel`: optional cheap model for auto-summ\r\nary; defaults to `agents.defaults.model.primary`.\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:212:  - Accepts `provider/model` or a configured model a\r\nlias.\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:213:- `modelOverrides`: allow the model to emit TTS dire\r\nctives (on by default).\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:336:- skips TTS if the reply already contains media or a\r\n `MEDIA:` directive.\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:337:- skips very short replies (< 10 chars).\r\n> F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:338:- summarizes long replies when enabled using `agents\r\n.defaults.model.primary` (or `summaryModel`).\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:339:- attaches the generated audio to the reply.\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:340:\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:354:                   yes -> summary enabled?\r\n  F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\o