{"type":"message","id":"8212e3e9","parentId":"9fd793b6","timestamp":"2026-03-10T17:08:22.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了！配置应该在 `agents.defaults` 节点下，而且现在配置已经包含了 `subagents.maxConcurrent`。之前我把它移到 `execution` 是错误的，因为 OpenClaw 不识别这个节点。\n\n现在配置已经恢复到正确的位置了，而且 gateway 已经在重启中。让我确认一下当前状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在明白了！配置应该在 **`agents.defaults`** 节点下，这是正确的。\n\n**正确的配置结构：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\"\n      },\n      \"models\": { ... },\n      \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\28964\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      },\n      \"maxConcurrent\": 10,\n      \"subagents\": {\n        \"maxConcurrent\": 8\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**说明：**\n- ✅ `agents.defaults.workspace` — 工作目录\n- ✅ `agents.defaults.compaction.mode` — 会话压缩策略\n- ✅ `agents.defaults.maxConcurrent` — 最大并发数\n- ✅ `agents.defaults.subagents.maxConcurrent` — 子代理最大并发数\n\n我之前移到 `execution` 是错的，OpenClaw 不识别这个节点。现在已经恢复正确了，配置验证通过 ✅\n\nGateway 正在重启中，稍等一下应该就好了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773162497686}}
