{"type":"message","id":"b767ed8d","parentId":"560bf3c8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T17:09:22.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！找到了 Zod schema 定义。现在可以确认配置结构了。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**有 schema！** OpenClaw 使用 Zod 定义配置 schema。\n\n根据 `zod-schema.agents.d.ts`，**`agents.defaults`** 节点下支持这些配置：\n\n```typescript\nagents.defaults: {\n  // 模型配置\n  model: { primary, fallbacks }\n  models: { ... }\n  \n  // 工作目录\n  workspace: string\n  \n  // 会话压缩\n  compaction: {\n    mode: \"default\" | \"safeguard\"\n    reserveTokens: number\n    keepRecentTokens: number\n    maxHistoryShare: number\n    ...\n  }\n  \n  // 并发控制\n  maxConcurrent: number\n  subagents: {\n    maxConcurrent: number\n    maxSpawnDepth: number\n    ...\n  }\n  \n  // 还有很多其他配置...\n  memorySearch, contextPruning, heartbeat, sandbox, tools, etc.\n}\n```\n\n**总结：**\n\n| 配置项 | 正确位置 |\n|--------|----------|\n| `workspace` | ✅ `agents.defaults.workspace` |\n| `compaction.mode` | ✅ `agents.defaults.compaction.mode` |\n| `maxConcurrent` | ✅ `agents.defaults.maxConcurrent` |\n| `subagents.maxConcurrent` | ✅ `agents.defaults.subagents.maxConcurrent` |\n\n**❌ 不存在 `execution` 节点** — 这是我之前的错误判断。\n\n你现在的配置已经是正确的了，在 `agents.defaults` 下。Schema 是动态验证的（通过 Zod），没有单独的 JSON Schema 文件暴露给用户，但可以通过 `openclaw config validate` 来验证配置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773162552887}}
